title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show FEB-12-2014 WED
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show FEB-12-2014 WED...PODCAST




The Glenn Beck Program



          Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET


        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 2/12/14Wednesday, February 12, 2014 




Glenn kicks off the show with a scathing response 
   from the owners of The Washington Redskins, in regards to 
     lawmakers demanding they change the team name, this is one you've got to hear.

  Also, a look at the state of the stock market in 1929 just before the crash and today,
          reveals a frightening resemblance.

  Plus, Katrina Pierson joins the program to discuss her run for Congress for the great state of Texas.
